{"TopicId":176711,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Is there a Mk0 fairing mod?","CreatedByName":"Fireheart318","CreatedById":159932,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-13T19:07:25Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Fireheart318","CreatedById":159932,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-13T19:07:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a mod that adds fairings that fit on\u00A0Mk0/0.625m parts? And no, Tweakscale doesn\u0027t work on fairings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nightside","CreatedById":150244,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-14T04:06:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223415067\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022176711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221531508845\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022159932\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fireheart318\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Fireheart318 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a mod that adds fairings that fit on\u00A0Mk0/0.625m parts? And no, Tweakscale doesn\u0027t work on fairings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can do it with Module Manager, but it is much trickier than rescaling a typical part.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019ve made bigger ones before, not smaller, but it should be doable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nightside","CreatedById":150244,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-14T16:47:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E//***Size 0 PAYLOAD FAIRINGS***\n//Does not rescale autotrusses.\n@PART[fairingSize1]\n{\t\n\t@MODEL,0 \n\t{\t\n\t\t\u0026amp;scale = 1.0, 1.0, 1.0\n\t\t@scale[*] *= 0.5\n\t}\n\t\n\t@node_stack_top,1 *= 0.5\n\t@node_stack_bottom,1 *= 0.5\n\t\n\t//fx_gasBurst_white = 0.0, 0.3, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 0.0, deploy\n\t\n\t@name = customFairingSize0\n\t@entryCost = 2000\n\t@cost = 200\n\t@title = AE-FF0 Airstream Protective Shell (0.625m)\n\t\n\t@MODULE[ModuleProceduralFairing]\n\t{\n\t\t@baseRadius *= 0.5\n\t\t@maxRadius *= 0.5\n\t\t@capRadius *= 0.5\n\t\t@xSectionHeightMax *= 0.5\n\t\t//UnitAreaMass = 0.016 \n\t\t//UnitAreaCost = 18 \n\t}\n\t@MODULE[ModuleCargoBay]  //not sure what this does\n\t{\n\t\t@lookupRadius *= 0.5\n\t}\t\n}\t\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis should get you started.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fireheart318","CreatedById":159932,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-11T20:11:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223415565\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022176711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221531586874\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150244\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nightside\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/14/2018 at 11:47 AM, Nightside said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E//***Size 0 PAYLOAD FAIRINGS***\n//Does not rescale autotrusses.\n@PART[fairingSize1]\n{\t\n\t@MODEL,0 \n\t{\t\n\t\t\u0026amp;scale = 1.0, 1.0, 1.0\n\t\t@scale[*] *= 0.5\n\t}\n\t\n\t@node_stack_top,1 *= 0.5\n\t@node_stack_bottom,1 *= 0.5\n\t\n\t//fx_gasBurst_white = 0.0, 0.3, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 0.0, deploy\n\t\n\t@name = customFairingSize0\n\t@entryCost = 2000\n\t@cost = 200\n\t@title = AE-FF0 Airstream Protective Shell (0.625m)\n\t\n\t@MODULE[ModuleProceduralFairing]\n\t{\n\t\t@baseRadius *= 0.5\n\t\t@maxRadius *= 0.5\n\t\t@capRadius *= 0.5\n\t\t@xSectionHeightMax *= 0.5\n\t\t//UnitAreaMass = 0.016 \n\t\t//UnitAreaCost = 18 \n\t}\n\t@MODULE[ModuleCargoBay]  //not sure what this does\n\t{\n\t\t@lookupRadius *= 0.5\n\t}\t\n}\t\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis should get you started.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I finally got around to adding the fairing to the game and it works great, except the base is slightly ahead of the rest of the fairing and it just doesn\u0027t look that great. What should I do to fix it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Norcalplanner","CreatedById":112223,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-15T06:39:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBDB has 0.625m custom fairings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AKerbalDog","CreatedById":219235,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-12T00:29:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223434021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022176711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221534315165\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022112223\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Norcalplanner\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/15/2018 at 4:39 PM, Norcalplanner said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBDB has 0.625m custom fairings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is BDB?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-12T01:02:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224090565\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022176711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644625769\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219235\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AKerbalDog\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n30 minutes ago, AKerbalDog said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is BDB?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022105588\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8181067425\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/122020-112x-bluedog-design-bureau-stockalike-saturn-apollo-and-more-v190-%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B1%D0%B5-13dec2021/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is a mod that adds lots of very nice parts to the game\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AKerbalDog","CreatedById":219235,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-12T01:11:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224090579\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022176711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644627733\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022136468\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Randazzo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Randazzo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022105588\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9262163621\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/122020-112x-bluedog-design-bureau-stockalike-saturn-apollo-and-more-v190-%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B1%D0%B5-13dec2021/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is a mod that adds lots of very nice parts to the game\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to just get the 0.625m fairing by deleting some of its parts? Whats the part name? I tried to get a 0.625m fairing but ended up breaking my game instead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-12T01:45:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224090585\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022176711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644628313\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219235\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AKerbalDog\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, AKerbalDog said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to just get the 0.625m fairing by deleting some of its parts? Whats the part name? I tried to get a 0.625m fairing but ended up breaking my game instead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/219235-akerbaldog/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022219235\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/219235-akerbaldog/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@AKerbalDog\u003C/a\u003E Give this a try: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/byoake9bfb5c44u/BDB%20Fairings.zip?dl=1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/byoake9bfb5c44u/BDB Fairings.zip?dl=1\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI pruned it for you, but those fairings are not quite the same as stock. Released under the same CC-BY-NC-SA 4.0 as the original Bluedog Design Bureau by Cobaltwolf.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the event you need a little guidance on installing mods:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022187982\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1233733807\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/182950-tutorial-how-to-install-mods-manually-ckan/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-02-12T03:16:28Z\u0022 title=\u002202/12/2022 03:16  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 12, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Randazzo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeadJohn","CreatedById":201293,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-12T03:26:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you just need fairings, use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E (a mod manager that runs outside KSP) to install \u0022Simple Adjustable Fairings - KW Rocketry fairing pack\u0022 (I might be a little off on the name).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat will give you great set of pretty fairings in 0.625 plus other sizes. It\u0027s a small mod even if you don\u0027t need those other sizes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}